Package org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.centerstage.robothardware

Class RobotHardware

java.lang.Object
org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.centerstage.RobotHardware
public class RobotHardware extends Object
Initializes hardware variables. Makes it so that one function call is required in our teleop and autonomous files to get hardware variables.
Author:
Nathan W
